first in the html file you will be given what is the quiz made of
i.e., the head where you get intoduced to it.
and the theme of the web page is given through the css file .

In this file;
backround theme is selected.
font is selected for page.
The quiz container box and question box and option boxes and next question box are dimensioned.
Specific Text colour for Title,question and option buttons are given.

In body:
The format of question and options and next question buttons are given
These questions are loaded from one javascript file and 
The loading of questions are given in another javascript file.

In this file :
you can load the next question only if you answer tha present one.
If it's correct you get 10 points.
And if it's wrong you get a message of correct answer and the next one is loaded.
you can't skip any of them.

For the last question you get a finish button instead of next question button.
And when you click finsh after answering...You will get your score out of 100.
